1. *Shvatio* sam da je pravi put koji treba da krenem. (I understood that the right path I should take.)
2. On je *shvatio* da je u pravu. (He realized that he was right.)
3. *Shvatajući* svoje greške, treba da pokušam da ih ispravim. (Understanding my mistakes, I should try to correct them.)
4. On je *shvatao* da je to veoma važno. (He realized that it was very important.)
5. Nisam *shvatio* do kraja šta je on hteo da kaže. (I didn't understand what he wanted to say entirely.)